      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Bojun Guo</b>\n</p><p><b>Bojun Guo</b>, (alias noobpwnftw)<br />\na Caribbean pirate<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>, computer chess and computer <a href=\"/Chinese_Chess\" title=\"Chinese Chess\">Xiangqi</a> developer, supporter and sponsor, as well as active member in <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">computer chess forums</a> and <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Social_media\">social media</a>.\nHe donates high-quality hardware for some communities such as <a href=\"/Stockfish#Fishtest\" title=\"Stockfish\">Fishtest</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>,\n<a href=\"/OpenBench\" title=\"OpenBench\">OpenBench</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>, <a href=\"/TCEC\" title=\"TCEC\">TCEC</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>, and <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\"> Talkchess</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#7-man_Syzygy_Bases\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">7-man Syzygy Bases</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Cloud_Databases\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Cloud Databases</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2016_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2016 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2020_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2020 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"7-man_Syzygy_Bases\">7-man Syzygy Bases</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bojun_Guo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: 7-man Syzygy Bases\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p>In an 5-month attempt in 2018 - supported by <a href=\"/Ronald_de_Man\" title=\"Ronald de Man\">Ronald de Man</a> -  Bojun Guo has generated all <a href=\"/Syzygy_Bases#7-man\" title=\"Syzygy Bases\">7-men tables</a> of <a href=\"/Syzygy_Bases\" title=\"Syzygy Bases\">Syzygy Bases</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Cloud_Databases\">Cloud Databases</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bojun_Guo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Cloud Databases\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p>Bojun Guo is author of the <a href=\"/index.php?title=Chess_Cloud_Database_Query_Interface&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Chess Cloud Database Query Interface (page does not exist)\">Chess Cloud Database Query Interface</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup> \nand the <a href=\"/index.php?title=Xiangqi_Cloud_Database_Query_Interface&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Xiangqi Cloud Database Query Interface (page does not exist)\">Xiangqi Cloud Database Query Interface</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup>.\nThe <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/API\">APIs</a> will provide online position analysis as well as <a href=\"/Endgame_Tablebases\" title=\"Endgame Tablebases\">EGTB</a> results where available \n<sup id=\"cite_ref-9\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bojun_Guo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2016_...\">2016 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bojun_Guo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2016 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=62639\">Cumulative building of a shared search tree</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Bojun Guo</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 28, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Opening_Book\" title=\"Opening Book\">Opening Book</a>, <a href=\"/Persistent_Hash_Table\" title=\"Persistent Hash Table\">Persistent Hash Table</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=64030&amp;start=11\">Re: Probe EGT in quiescence?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Bojun Guo</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 21, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Endgame_Tablebases\" title=\"Endgame Tablebases\">Endgame Tablebases</a>, <a href=\"/Quiescence_Search\" title=\"Quiescence Search\">Quiescence Search</a>, <a href=\"/Chinese_Chess\" title=\"Chinese Chess\">Xiangqi</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=66797\">7-men Syzygy attempt</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Bojun Guo</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 10, 2018</li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=66797&amp;start=472\">Re: 7-men Syzygy attempt</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Bojun Guo</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 19, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/Syzygy_Bases#7-man\" title=\"Syzygy Bases\">7-men Syzygy Bases</a></dd></dl>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://lichess.org/@/lichess/blog/7-piece-syzygy-tablebases-are-complete/W3WeMyQA\">7-piece Syzygy tablebases are complete</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Lichess&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Lichess (page does not exist)\">Lichess</a>, August 19, 2018</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=66824&amp;start=79\">Re: LCZero update</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Bojun Guo</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 16, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/Leela_Chess_Zero\" title=\"Leela Chess Zero\">Leela Chess Zero</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=66886&amp;start=1\">Re: comparing minimax and averaging MCTS with alphabeta rollouts</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Bojun Guo</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 20, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/Monte-Carlo_Tree_Search\" title=\"Monte-Carlo Tree Search\">Monte-Carlo Tree Search</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=68253&amp;start=190\">Re: Chess.com 2018 computer chess championship</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Bojun Guo</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 16, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/Thread\" title=\"Thread\">Thread</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=69175&amp;start=170\">Re: Alphazero news</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Bojun Guo</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 10, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/AlphaZero\" title=\"AlphaZero\">AlphaZero</a></li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=69175&amp;start=299\">Re: Alphazero news</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Bojun Guo</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 15, 2018</dd></dl>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=71386\">Database snapshot</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">noobpwnftw</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 27, 2019</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=71764\">ChessDBCN</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">noobpwnftw</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 09, 2019</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=72137\">Ryzen problems - AGAIN!</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">noobpwnftw</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 22, 2019</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2020_...\">2020 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bojun_Guo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2020 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=72958&amp;start=5\">Re: Chess Cloud Database Query Interface</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">noobpwnftw</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 01, 2020&#160;» <a href=\"/index.php?title=Chess_Cloud_Database_Query_Interface&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Chess Cloud Database Query Interface (page does not exist)\">Chess Cloud Database Query Interface</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=73406&amp;start=18\">Re: Poor mans testing process please</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">noobpwnftw</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 22, 2020</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=73481&amp;start=7\">Re: Using Freeware AI and Dynamically Generated Endgame Tablebases</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">noobpwnftw</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 28, 2020&#160;» <a href=\"/FinalGen\" title=\"FinalGen\">FinalGen</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=75247&amp;start=123\">Re: A Crossroad in Computer Chess; Or Desperate Flailing for Relevance</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">noobpwnftw</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 05, 2020</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bojun_Guo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/noobpwnftw\">noobpwnftw (Bojun Guo)· GitHub</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">noobpwnftw</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.chessdb.cn/queryc_en/\">Chess Cloud Database Query Interface</a></li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.chessdb.cn/cloudbookc_api_en.html\">Chess Cloud Database API Documentation</a></dd></dl>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.chessdb.cn/query_en/\">Xiangqi Cloud Database Query Interface</a></li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.chessdb.cn/cloudbook_api_en.html\">Xiangqi Cloud Database API Documentation</a></dd></dl>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bojun_Guo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://talkchess.com/viewtopic.php?p=970688#p970688\">Re: @CPW contributors</a> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Bojun Guo</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 25, 2024</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=72837\">Stockfish 11</a> by <a href=\"/Stephane_Nicolet\" title=\"Stephane Nicolet\">Stephane Nicolet</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 18, 2020</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"ex